msgstr "![スクリーンショット](/images/guide/css-components-previewer-02.png)"

#: /p/gh/OnsenUI/onsen.io/src/documents_en/v2/guide/theming.html:58
msgid ""
"The HTML code used in this example is defined by the following annotation "
